    "description": "Ledax Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the purchase, sale, and distribution of automobiles in Japan, Asia, Oceania, Africa, and internationally. It operates through Automobile distribution business, and Leaseback-related business segments. The company engages in the purchase and sale of used cars through its retail stores; sale of various property and casualty insurance products comprising car insurance; wholesale and distribution of spare parts and accessories of automobiles through online shop; management of automobile aftermarket parts of online distribution; and export of used cars through internet site, PicknBuy24.com. It also offers management consulting, M&A advisory, outsourcing, and investment services. The company was formerly known as Carchs Holdings Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Ledax Co.,Ltd. in September 2024. Ledax Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1977 and is based in Tokyo, Japan."
